metadata.name: SHAMANIC SESSIONS #01
metadata.description:
SHAMANIC SESSIONS #01

=

4500 x 5092 pixel jpeg

=

working with AI has something alchemical and shamanistic in digital contexts
a handling of substances, temperatures, feelings, deliberations and a subsequent fine-tuning

this series is dedicated to shamanists and alchemists, their experimental ways of working and their becoming and melting into substances

the series will be continuously extended with more and more high quality digitally generated works
